<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Check-in Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #16a34a;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Time to check in</h1>

  <p>This is a reminder to confirm you're still active on <%= @app_name %>.</p>

  <p><strong>Reminder attempt <%= @attempt_number %> of <%= @attempt_total %>.</strong></p>

  <% if @next_checkin_at %>
    <p>Your check-in is due by: <strong><%= @next_checkin_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %H:%M UTC") %></strong></p>
  <% end %>

  <p>
    <a href="<%= @checkin_url %>" class="button" style="color: #ffffff !important;">Confirm Check-in</a>
  </p>

  <p>
    If you don't check in, we'll keep sending reminders every <%= ((@user.effective_checkin_attempt_interval_hours) / 24.0).round %> days.
    If you still don't respond after the final reminder, your messages will be delivered.
  </p>

  <% if @next_attempt_at && @attempt_number < @attempt_total %>
    <p>Next reminder: <strong><%= @next_attempt_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %H:%M UTC") %></strong></p>
  <% end %>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message from <%= @app_name %>.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
